description: Schedules delivery of a configuration snapshot to the Amazon S3 bucket in the specified delivery channel. After the delivery has started, Config sends the following notifications using an Amazon SNS topic that you have specified.

parameters.name: deliveryChannelName
parameters.description: The name of the delivery channel through which the snapshot is delivered.

nested_items.name: configSnapshotId
nested_items.description: The ID of the snapshot that is being created.
